Instructions to run the application:

1) Download and unpack project zip.
2) Navigate to project directory and run the app with following command: "activator run". 
3) The application now will be accessible on http://localhost:9000/.
4) For the first time you visit the site, you will click "apply script now" (this version of the project uses in-memory database and script initializes it).
5) There are three types of users for this app: student, teacher and administrator. Sample accounts for each of them are as follows:
	o	teacher@mail.com	
	o	student@mail.com
	o	admin@mail.com
6) Password for all sample accounts is "password"



